products.unbrandedName: All-Day Neoprene Backpack
products.description: They say it’s all about work-life balance, right? That’s exactly what you’ll get in our All-Day Neoprene Backpack. With a built-in laptop sleeve, detachable pouch for valuables, and ample pockets to keep you organized, this backpack will be your go-to from 9-to-5 and beyond. Did we mention how much we’re loving the super flexible, recycled neoprene fabric and luggage-handle sleeve on the back? Trust us when we say this is the backpack you’ll use on the reg – whether you’re hitting the gym after work or zipping through the airport. This bag was made with the environment in mind, using materials made from up to 27 recycled, post-consumer plastic bottles.

products.name: All-Day Neoprene Backpack
products.brandedName: Quince All-Day Neoprene Backpack
products.unbrandedName: All-Day Neoprene Backpack
products.description: They say it’s all about work-life balance, right? That’s exactly what you’ll get in our All-Day Neoprene Backpack. With a built-in laptop sleeve, detachable pouch for valuables, and ample pockets to keep you organized, this backpack will be your go-to from 9-to-5 and beyond. Did we mention how much we’re loving the super flexible, recycled neoprene fabric and luggage-handle sleeve on the back? Trust us when we say this is the backpack you’ll use on the reg – whether you’re hitting the gym after work or zipping through the airport. This bag was made with the environment in mind, using materials made from up to 27 recycled, post-consumer plastic bottles.
